<div style="font-family:Amatic SC; background: #FF7700; color: #FFFFFF; border:3px solid #000000; box-shadow: 0px 0px 7px #000000; padding:5px 10px; margin:1em; text-align:center;"><font size="5">Settlements</font></div>
Due to '''Level 0.22's''' non-linear geometry and isolation effect, creating a settlement of any form is impossible.

<div style="font-family:Amatic SC; background: #FF7700; color: #FFFFFF; border:3px solid #000000; box-shadow: 0px 0px 7px #000000; padding:5px 10px; margin:1em; text-align:center;"><font size="5">Entrances and Exits</font></div>
===Entrances===

*Rarely, finding a door on [[Level 0]] labeled "Work In Progress" will lead you here.
*Entering a building that is under construction on [[Level 11]] or [[Level 111]] will bring one to this level.
*Various unknown factors in [[Level 0.23]] may lead back here.

===Exits===

*Going through an exit door will lead you to [[Level 27]] or back to [[Level 0]].
*Various unknown factors may lead to [[Level 0.23]].

